high_descs: Turn left and take a step, then turn left again and walk up to the toaster on the kitchen counter.
Pick up the tomato that is to the left of the toaster.
Turn around and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the tomato inside, then close the door.
Turn left and walk over to the white table that has a loaf of bread on it.
Pick up the tomato that is on the white table.
Turn right and walk back over to the microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the tomato inside.
Turn around and walk over to the area of kitchen counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle.
Turn around and walk back over to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, slice up both tomatoes, then close the door of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice up two tomatoes in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the toaster.

Place the tomato in the microwave.
Turn to your left and walk to the table on your right.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Walk back to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
Turn around and walk toward the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Walk back to the microwave.
Open the microwave and flip over each object inside the microwave then close it.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a knife while two tomatoes cook in the microwave.
